  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"Witness True Power\" By facing the most powerful boss of all time.. Terror Terius!</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972750/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.poster.avif?t=1755720035\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972750/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.webm?t=1755720035\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972750/extras/0d3de820b1dd38b98520dcce0c33ac5a.mp4?t=1755720035\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Continue DNA in part two of the boss battle against Terius within the final episode, following the journey of Leo where Terius's true form has finally been revealed...Terror Terius!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972750/extras/64bf063c2aa5d8dd5d2d7b72d11d3d06.avif?t=1755720035\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Face True Terror...</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Resume the Epic Battle between Leo and Terius!<br><br></li><li>Has Leo's end come? Find out on the next Episode of DNA: Final Episode: Part 2!<br><br></li><li> Clash with darkness and discover the fate of the world...</li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972750/extras/37b62fbf84c69e9238183bfdac8512e8.avif?t=1755720035\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Battle the True Evil Within Terius...</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pick back up this episode with DNA's epic 2D Beat'em up gameplay!<br><br></li><li>Experience a challenging gameplay formula building upon last season's rewarding difficulties.<br><br></li><li> Take Terius head on in part two of the epic showdown...</li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972750/extras/baa23427dd07769e189809728b56659f.avif?t=1755720035\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Clash with the Heart of Darkness.</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Watch as the story develops further into intriguing events in part two of the final episode of DNA.<br><br></li><li> Engage in battle with Terius to avenge all of the scars left by his hatred towards mankind.<br><br></li><li> Can Leo survive against the final form of Terror Terius...? </li></ul></i>",
