son's rewarding difficulties.<br><br></li><li> Take Terius head on in part two of the epic showdown...</li></ul></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972750/extras/baa23427dd07769e189809728b56659f.avif?t=1755720035\" width=616 height=308 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Clash with the Heart of Darkness.</strong></h2><br><i><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Watch as the story develops further into intriguing events in part two of the final episode of DNA.<br><br></li><li> Engage in battle with Terius to avenge all of the scars left by his hatred towards mankind.<br><br></li><li> Can Leo survive against the final form of Terror Terius...? </li></ul></i>",
